premise_source_doc_sentence: Klute is a 1971 American neo-noir crime-thriller film directed and produced by Alan J. Pakula , written by Andy and Dave Lewis , and starring Jane Fonda , Donald Sutherland , Charles Cioffi , and Roy Scheider .
Daniel O'Donnell Klute  (  1921 -- 1964  )  was an American rocket scientist and chemical engineer .
